# <emoji> <type>(<scope>): <short title>

# ---------------------
# Commit Message Guide
# ---------------------
# Emoji + Type (required):
#   ✨ feat(scope):     A new feature
#   🐛 fix(scope):      A bug fix
#   📝 docs(scope):     Documentation changes
#   🎨 style(scope):    Code style (no logic changes)
#   ♻️ refactor(scope): Refactoring without behavior changes
#   ⚡ perf(scope):      Performance improvements
#   ✅ test(scope):     Adding or updating tests
#   🔧 chore(scope):    Maintenance tasks (build, CI, tooling, etc.)
#   🚑 hotfix(scope):   Urgent production fixes
#
# Scope (required):
#   The area/module impacted (e.g., auth, api, db, ui, payment).
#
# Title (required):
#   Keep it concise, max 72 characters.
#
# Description (optional):
#   Add details about what and why below, after a blank line.
#
# ---------------------
# Example:
# 🐛 fix(auth): handle null tokens
#
# Added null checks to prevent crashes when user tokens are missing.